{"tid":1198343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日好多謝有份開咗東行車線嘅朋友","createTime":"2019-06-10T08:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:07:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f34fd31d6bbb30362ac5cb3c687d9ac0f30658b","tid":1198343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:03:24.000Z","msg":"琴日好多謝有份開咗東行車線嘅朋友，<br />\n依家開晒東西行線都要夜晚10點幾龍尾先行到終點，<br />\n你話唔開埋要行到幾點 ？<br />\n<br />\n親眼見都有兩個遊行人仕 需要救護員救護離開， 一個面都變白晒要係右邊要警察剪開鐵欄離開休息（ 麥當勞對出怡和街）(當時已開咗東西行車線行)。<br />\n<br />\n 唔係你哋開咗嘅話會再有幾多人體力不支暈倒 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝你哋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日真係好多好多人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa